{"tid":626673,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"689「幫口」UGL案眾籌吸百萬","createTime":"2018-04-12T10:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T00:31:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"931de1d483668d4c80fed3af7b048fc8d41c09a2","tid":626673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359233?_ga=2.44073892.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359233%3F_ga%3D2.44073892.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=jWlCGUlyUx1sda%2BvdaxSjLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=14fe205f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359233%3F_ga%3D2.44073892.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=9fe9a243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359233?_ga=2.44073892.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：689「幫口」UGL案眾籌吸百萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180412/large/0411mike0021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F0411mike0021.jpg&h=83923e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林卓廷<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n民主黨發起「天下為公」眾籌查前特首梁振英UGL涉貪案，大嗱嗱200萬，喺今時今日社會運動氣氛低迷嘅時候，真係唔多令人樂觀。但呢個計劃公佈咗幾日，至噚晚11點就籌到超過100萬，已經達成目標一半。<br />\n<br />\n有份搞呢個計劃嘅民主黨林卓廷指市民反應踴躍，甚至有街坊拎埋錢上佢議辦話捐錢，反映大家都好想追查事件真相，只不過佢哋眾籌係唔收現金，惟有婉拒好意，或者都再諗吓有乜網上外嘅其他方法接收捐款。<br />\n<br />\n而阿廷噚日返立法會途中，都有市民同佢講起「天下為公」呢個計劃，叫佢哋畀心機、加油，可見市民反應幾好。<br />\n<br />\n市民咁大反應，可能要多謝梁振英，君不見自從梁振英出聲明鬧阿廷、之後出埋律師信後，群情更洶湧，據聞連海外嘅港人都打畀阿廷話支持，所以呢，689真係「天下為公」嘅啦啦隊隊長呀。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：小麗搵Plan B　楊彧係心水 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：補選滿月　陳家珮「晉身」立會 (李八方)"},{"pid":"24d04d6fab667803548af937b55afa8cae73d859","tid":626673,"uid":11217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26cf53e75b2f119e7daf0e13903fcd91d52d2b68","tid":626673,"uid":11217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26b696ae99dff98ef8c2ec09e50b68c462637e0e","tid":626673,"uid":11217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98ab58d41d1170bd8b06e584ee0fb104820e1878","tid":626673,"uid":11217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fffacf84b14bf1d12579af28a94e83c1638018fd","tid":626673,"uid":11217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}